# `ParamStr(N)` argv access (no parsing), and
# from the `getopts` library on Object Pascal /
# Lazarus.  Extends cross-language CLI taxonomy
# to FIFTY-ONE library variants: Rust (6), Go (4),
# Python (3), Crystal 1 OptionParser (R269),
